{"tid":1743962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致仲係poly入面既手足（二）","createTime":"2019-11-21T12:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T13:38:53.000Z","uid":269125,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9f246c176b74d6de75cf2e65452c7cc9be535760","tid":1743962,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:44:30.000Z","msg":"又係我。<br />\n一開始都係要再講，你地捱咁多日已經做得好好，如果捱唔住真係可以出嚟，無人會怪你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果你地仲想繼續捱落去，請考慮下<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">開記者會</span></strong>。<br />\n你可能話開記者會講咩好呀？<br />\n其實講咩都唔緊要，重點唔係你地講咩。<br />\n但我都可以俾少少意見，好簡單，例如講以下既野就好：<br />\n「我地無做錯任何事，所以唔會投降。請警方如果認為我地犯法，就衝入嚟，用棍用槍用暴力制伏我地，將我地從學校入面拖到街上面去。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好，返正題，真正重要既事係，當你地開記者會時，地點要選係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">飯堂</span></strong>。並且其他手足請係所有媒體燈光下開始<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>清潔飯堂</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n點解咁重要？因為呢兩日每一個入過去既權貴、機構們都不約而同話入面衛生情況惡劣，製造大家只會破壞，不如出嚟既輿論環境。<br />\n所以你地要係鏡頭面前，大肆破壞佢地想要製造出來既混亂畫面。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Show them. We are hongkongers, we fight with discipline.</span></strong></span><br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0811195e1975fa7126a1e8928b537896810f248a","tid":1743962,"uid":257736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:47:30.000Z","msg":"開記招 is ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2863f8c51c5cf852e88473cc0a5ffa525aea77","tid":1743962,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355dbff1109f8563fe5ccd238da53407d8ac9e15","tid":1743962,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"當然大家有咩意見都可以提出"}]}